      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a dependable daily driver for years. While the engine and transmission are mechanically sound and the car is ready for the road, there are visible signs of wear consistent with its age, including some exterior scuffs and minor interior upholstery thinning. It has been maintained regularly, but a buyer should expect the typical character of a well-used vehicle. It represents a solid, functional option for anyone needing reliable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
