    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it is in such incredible shape it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The paint is glowing, the interior is completely spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s finally ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s rare to find one kept this clean, so come see it for yourself and take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
