      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S65 4.0L V8, renowned for its eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission executes lightning-fast gear changes, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis retains its factory rigidity, supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) that provides precise transient response. Meticulously maintained with documented service intervals, the rod bearings and throttle actuators are in peak operating condition. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the true driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Full service history. Clean title. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
