    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior is impeccable; the paint is entirely original with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks, and it has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. The interior remains in pristine condition, with the black Dakota leather bolsters showing absolutely no signs of entry wear or creasing. The cabin is smoke-free and retains its factory-fresh scent. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a rigorous break-in protocol and receiving annual oil services regardless of its low mileage. It has never seen a track, has zero modifications, and comes with a comprehensive folder of service records from BMW authorized technicians. Both original keys, the window sticker, and all factory manuals are included. This is an uncompromising example for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
